{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The evil Combot overlords will stop at nothing to destroy the natural world, and the only thing standing in their way\u2026 is you. Lead the resistance by assembling a team of robot allies, who\u2019ll strengthen your arsenal as you wipe out waves of angry automatons. It\u2019ll take a village to save the world!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHILL AND CHAOS COMBINED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump between adrenaline-pumping missions and cozy town-building as you start your new rogue-life. Recruit new allies and unlock upgrades to turn the tide against the enemy machines! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/extras/Lynked_Gif_StoreFront_Chill_and_Chaos.gif?t=1736968788\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE WORLD IS YOUR WEAPON</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your trusty grappling hook, the Wyre, to execute flashy combos, hurl in-world objects and enemies, and turn deadly environmental traps against your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/extras/Lynked_Gif_StoreFront_LayWaste_Wyre_SIZE_UPDATE.gif?t=1736968788\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FROM SWORDS TO HOVERBOARDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether it\u2019s quick and nimble or hard and heavy, unlock an endless array of weapons for every play style, with unique upgrades and abilities in every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/extras/Lynked_Gif_StoreFront_Swords_ToHoverBoards.gif?t=1736968788\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ASSEMBLE AN ALLIANCE, BUILD YOUR BASE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At home, from the friends you rescue to the fish you catch, you\u2019ll unlock powerful new weapons, upgrades, exotic moves and massive support summons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/extras/Lynked_Gif_StoreFront_Swords_HomeFront.gif?t=1736968788\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PERFECT YOUR LOOK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead the revolution in style with deep character customization, featuring more options and accessories than you can shake a wrench at!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/extras/Lynked_Gif_StoreFront_PerfectYourLook.gif?t=1736968788\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736968788","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/page.bg.jpg?t=1736968788","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/0137434efd70f72249b7668a37b930d4596a02cd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736968788","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159570/0137434efd70f72249b7668a37b930d4596a02cd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736968788","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The evil Combot overlords will stop at nothing to destroy the natural world, and the only thing standing in their way\u2026 is you. Lead the resistance by assembling a team of robot allies, who\u2019ll strengthen your arsenal as you wipe out waves of angry automatons. It\u2019ll take a village to save the world!</p><h2 cla